  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to evaluate the safety and tolerability of multi-dose,
      open-label LX606 in subjects with symptomatic carcinoid syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
